name: Eternal Equinox
body:
#Introduction
Eternal Equinox, the first game of Rejected Domination series, solely developed by Alexander James, also formely known as AJtheprogrammer.

#Story
A despicable hater finds himself on a world of liberation and fantastic people. Meanwhile, a Dreamweaver finds himself trapped in his own wrath.

#Information
Game Type: NicoRaptor Danmaku
Game Number: #1
